title: NaturaSi - Via San Giovanni Evangelista
description: Popular health and organic chain of stores in Italy. Sells only organic products many items that are suitable for vegans, including tofu and seitan products, cookies and cakes without eggs, milk or butter, etc). Fresh organic bread every day.
streetAddress: Via San Giovanni Evangelista (1 tronco) n. 7 - 7/A, Spezzano di Fiorano Modenese
